,"arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ لَوْ أَنَّ لَهُم مَّا فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ جَمِيعًۭا وَمِثْلَهُۥ مَعَهُۥ لِيَفْتَدُوا۟ بِهِۦ مِنْ عَذَابِ يَوْمِ ٱلْقِيَٰمَةِ مَا تُقُبِّلَ مِنْهُمْ ۖ وَلَهُمْ عَذَابٌ أَلِيمٌۭ","translation":"Verily, if those who are bent on denying the truth had all that is on earth, and twice as much, to offer as ransom from suffering on the Day of Resurrection, it would not be accepted from them: for grievous suffering awaits them.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/705.mp3","surahId":5,"words":[{"id":38249,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/005_036_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38250,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_036_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38251,"position":3,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","translation":"অবিশ্বাস করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_036_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38252,"position":4,"arabic":"لَوْ","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/005_036_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38253,"position":5,"arabic":"أَنَّ","translation":"হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/005_036_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38254,"position":6,"arabic":"لَهُم","translation":"জন্যে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_036_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38255,"position":7,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"যা কিছু","audioUrl":"wbw/005_036_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38256,"position":8,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/005_036_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38257,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/005_036_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38258,"position":10,"arabic":"جَمِيعًۭا","translation":"সমস্তই","audioUrl":"wbw/005_036_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38259,"position":11,"arabic":"وَمِثْلَهُۥ","translation":"ও সমতুল্য তার(আরও কিছু)","audioUrl":"wbw/005_036_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38260,"position":12,"arabic":"مَعَهُۥ","translation":"সাথে তার",